description:
This is a 15 minute workout called '15 min METABOLIC BOOSTING cycling workout' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Cycling.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Endorphin Wave and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Do this ride every morning to boost your metabolism and start your day off in a positive way! This 15 minute cycling workout will make an energizing addition to your day! This ride is perfect if you want a low-intensity ride on an active recovery day or if you are in the mood for a high-intensity push to really get your sweat on. You can also add this ride before any workout to get your mojo flowing and your mind in the game! It might be hard to push play, but I know by the end of this ride, you will be so happy you did! 

Cheers and chug to an awesome day ahead! Make it an amazing one! Thanks for working out with me!

IMPORTANT! The RPMs noted throughout the ride are just a range! Make sure to ride where you feel comfortable! That may be above or below the range indicated. If you'd like to make this ride a bit more intense, you can always work at a higher RPM. 

Need a longer WARM-UP?  https://youtu.be/tOjKOmtPcqs
